{"tid":2174920,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西龜問題 求救","createTime":"2020-08-26T07:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T16:52:03.000Z","uid":239013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4abf9c36bbf06871565da93781a1c4f5077f5a96","tid":2174920,"uid":239013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"屋企養咗兩隻巴西龜<br />\n養左差唔多20幾年 一係和平相處<br />\n但唔知點解最近大嗰隻(女仔) 有時會想咬細嗰隻 (男仔)<br />\n可能係因為男龜成日煩住女龜<br />\n<br />\n但係檢查過都冇咬過有傷口<br />\n已經分開咗兩個盆養<br />\n但係因為share同一個露台<br />\n有時佢哋會入咗同一個盆<br />\n所以唔知係咪因為咁<br />\n今日幫佢哋檢查嗰陣 發現男龜條尾下面有個紅色點<br />\n唔知係咪打交整到定係病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇大師可以解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504473a04798ee4079e484514ec3c86b6041d9f0","tid":2174920,"uid":21550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba13d46065f781fa655e2b57f3ff8d12f052378","tid":2174920,"uid":239013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"504473a04798ee4079e484514ec3c86b6041d9f0","tid":2174920,"uid":21550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係 <br />\n女仔一啲都唔親人 <br />\n反而男仔嗰隻摸佢下巴嗰啲都冇事<br />\n以為佢哋養埋一齊咁多年應該唔會打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8ff3cef3ec23ed58b6a4142bc5435b353a25d3","tid":2174920,"uid":16574